Subject: [PATCH] Settings: Add root access manager to developer options
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Add SuAccessFragment with per-app toggles for root (su) access.
Writes UIDs to /data/local/su_whitelist (world-readable).
Alphabetical section headers, show/hide system apps toggle.

Pure AOSP Settings — no LineageOS-specific dependencies.

